text: Jip van den Bos (born 12 April 1996) is a Dutch professional racing cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's Continental Team . Ahead of the 2021 season, van den Bos joined , forming part of the team's inaugural roster. ==Major results== ;2014 :4th Road Race, UEC European Junior Road Championship ;2015 :7th Ronde van Gelderland :8th Salverda Omloop van de IJsseldelta ;2016 :1st 20px Young rider classification Emakumeen Euskal Bira :6th Overall Tour of Chongming Island ::1st 20px Young rider classification :8th Omloop van het Hageland ;2017 :4th Omloop van Borsele ;2018 :2nd Rabobank 7-Dorpenomloop Aalburg ;2019 :1st Le Samyn des Dames :3rd Omloop Het Nieuwsblad ==See also== * 2015 Parkhotel Valkenburg Continental Team season ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch female cyclists Category:People from Wormerland Category:Sportspeople from North Holland
